column5: I am with a group going up to Press Lake the first week in September and it is a new lake for our group. We have a lake map and have talked with one person who has fished this lake. Just wondering if anyone has any information on Press Lake? Anything at all would be helpful, thanks.

I like Press Lake. I met ggg (another WC member) there. Both of us gave the camp and fishing good reviews. I don't think you can get back to those threads but you can try searching for "Press Lake" in the Canada, Fishing report, and General discussion forums. If I can find the info I sent to some other WC members, I will send it along to you.
